---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-100 px-6 py-24 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[#2563EB]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 10c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3s3 1.343 3 3c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3s-3-1.343-3-3z"/><path d="M11 17c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3s3 1.343 3 3c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3s-3-1.343-3-3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-lg font-black tracking-tight text-[#1E293B] uppercase">
            Odonto<span class="text-[#2563EB]">Premium</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
          Reabilitando sorrisos e transformando vidas através da odontologia digital e humanizada. Excelência técnica e conforto absoluto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 mb-8">Serviços</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">
          <li class="hover:text-[#2563EB] transition-colors"><a href="#">Lentes de Contato</a></li>
          <li class="hover:text-[#2563EB] transition-colors"><a href="#">Implantes Digitais</a></li>
          <li class="hover:text-[#2563EB] transition-colors"><a href="#">Invisalign</a></li>
          <li class="hover:text-[#2563EB] transition-colors"><a href="#">Clareamento Laser</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 mb-8">Contato</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium">
          <li>(11) 99999-9999</li>
          <li>contato@odontopremium.com.br</li>
          <li>Av. Paulista, 1000 - CJ 101</li>
          <li>Bela Vista, São Paulo - SP</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 mb-8">RT</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Roberto Carvalho<br />
          CRO-SP 123.456<br />
          Especialista em Reabilitação Oral
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 pt-10 border-t border-slate-50 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 sm:flex-row">
      <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">
        © {currentYear} Odonto Premium. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="#" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-[#2563EB] transition-colors">Instagram</a>
        <a href="#" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-[#2563EB] transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
